metadata.name: Oculus
metadata.description:
In frame:

Oculus New York is a transportation hub located in Lower Manhattan, New York City. It is known for its iconic and futuristic architecture, designed by Spanish architect Santiago Calatrava.

Specifications:

Genre: Photography (Fine Art)
Artist: Kirit Prajapati (Photographer and colour version)
Collaborator: Syed Kafeel Gillani (Black and White version and animation)
Location: Oculus, New York
Photo Resolution: 5848 × 8772 px
Video Resolution: Full Resolution 4K available 
Year Captured: 2022

Licensing:

NFT holders can display the photograph in private and/or public galleries, for advertising and/or promotion purposes, as long as the creator is credited. Provides NO rights for commercial purpose, that includes, commercial distribution, creating commercial merchandise and derivative works.
